Locale-Babelfish version 0.01
=============================
Locale::Babelfish - wrapper between Locale::Maketext::Lexicon and Babelfish format

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

  Locale::Maketext
  Class::Accessor::Grouped
  YAML::Tiny
  Carp
  Modern::Perl

